data.description: Experience the epitome of serene living in this beautiful Riverfront Country French Estate. Designed to perfection, this captivating 2-story home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths & fabulous river frontage- offering the perfect blend of comfort & sophistication. The living room features enchanting river views & a quadrafire pellet stove. The charming kitchen w/pantry & cozy breakfast nook invite tranquility to your mornings. The spacious primary suite presents an idyllic sanctuary overlooking the river, complete w/jetted tub. Outdoors, the lush lawns invite leisurely strolls, while river irrigation ensures greenery all year round. With low bank access to the river, indulge in your passion for fishing or simply find solace in the natural beauty of the river. Detached 2 car garage & 1bed/1bath guest quarters. This space offers flexibility for extended family stays or a home office. All of this situated on 1.25 acres of coveted Rogue River frontage. Sq. Ft. includes guest quarter of 592-sq
